article.description: — Isiaih Mosley had 21 points as Missouri State romped past Sam Houston 77-55 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Mosley carries Missouri St. past Sam Houston St. 77-55
article.linkText: Mosley carries Missouri St. past Sam Houston St. 77-55
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- — Isiaih Mosley had 21 points as Missouri State romped past Sam Houston 77-55 on Wednesday night. Gaige Prim had 17 points and 13 rebounds for Missouri State (2-1). Ja'Monta Black added 15 points. Keaton Hervey had 11 points. Jarren Cook had 12 points for the Bearkats (1-2) as did Savion Flagg. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
